### Get All Roles
GET http://localhost:8000/api/role
Authorization: Bearer {{bearer_token}}

### Get Single Role
GET http://localhost:8000/api/role/1
Authorization: Bearer {{bearer_token}}

### Create New Role
POST http://localhost:8000/api/role
Authorization: Bearer {{bearer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "admin"
}

### Create Role with Guard
POST http://localhost:8000/api/role
Authorization: Bearer {{bearer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "api_user",
    "guard_name": "api"
}

### Update Role
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/role/1
Authorization: Bearer {{bearer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "updated_admin"
}

### Update Role with Guard
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/role/1
Authorization: Bearer {{bearer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "updated_api_user",
    "guard_name": "api"
}

### Delete Role
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/role/1
Authorization: Bearer {{bearer_token}}

